      <p class="section__eyebrow">Who sets it up</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading">A Certified ProAdvisor builds the financial foundation with you.</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>The checklist is everything a new business can do on its own &mdash; and many founders do, with clean software and a steady cadence. Where a Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor earns a place is in getting the foundation right so a year of transactions doesn&rsquo;t build on a crooked base: a chart of accounts sized to how the business actually works, the software connected correctly, opening balances that tie, and a reconciliation rhythm that holds. That work is done against a written scope, and the discovery call is free. We stay in our lane &mdash; the bookkeeping and financial operations &mdash; and send entity and tax decisions to your attorney and CPA, where they belong. Independent firm; not Intuit, and not Intuit&rsquo;s software support.</p>
